{"type":"message","id":"30fa83f8","parentId":"e5345952","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:04:59.632Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我直接在当前窗口发出来。根据说明，这是在 webchat 对话中。我应该把英文翻译直接发送出来。\n\n但是等等，主人说的是\"翻译并发出来\"，我已经获取了中文内容。我理解主人想要的是英文翻译版本。让我准备一个清晰的英文翻译。\n\n由于这是在 webchat 中回复，我不需要使用 message 工具，直接回复就可以。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人，英文翻译版本如下：\n\n---\n\n## US Stock Sell-off Devastates AI Giants, \"Magnificent Seven\" Market Cap Evaporates Over $850 Billion\n\nOver the past week, persistent rising inflation has intensified market concerns that interest rates will remain elevated for longer periods. Coupled with adverse factors facing individual companies, large-cap tech stocks have suffered severe setbacks.\n\nThe combined market capitalization of the \"Magnificent Seven\" evaporated by more than **$850 billion** over the past week.\n\n**Key Performance:**\n\n- **Meta** posted its worst weekly performance since October 2025, declining over 11% during the week. Earlier this week, the company lost a landmark social media lawsuit, and Wall Street continues to react to this development.\n\n- A jury ruled that Meta and Google (parent of YouTube) were negligent in failing to protect underage users on their platforms. Alphabet, Google's parent company, fell nearly 9% during the week.\n\n- **Microsoft** dropped 6.5% during the week and may face its worst quarterly performance since 2008. Software stocks were particularly hard hit.\n\n- **NVIDIA** and **Amazon** each fell approximately 3% during the week, while **Tesla** declined nearly 2% over five trading days.\n\n- The semiconductor sector rebounded on Friday, but Sandisk and Micron Technology still ended the week lower after sharp declines on Thursday.\n\n- Before this sell-off wave, Alphabet released new research findings, announcing an algorithm designed to reduce AI memory usage. This news triggered volatility in memory chips and the broader semiconductor sector.\n\nGrowth stocks were severely battered this week, impacted by surging oil prices pushing up inflation expectations and rising bond yields. Investors believe the Federal Reserve will not be able to cut rates this year as previously expected.\n\n**Apple (AAPL)** was the only stock among the \"Magnificent Seven\" to post a modest gain during the week. Reports this week indicated that Apple plans to open its Siri voice assistant to competing AI services beyond OpenAI's ChatGPT.\n\n---\n\n主人，翻译已完成！有什么其他需要琪琪帮忙的吗？🎀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1171,"output":594,"cacheRead":41984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43749,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774681489386}}
{"type":"message","id":"276d6462","parentId":"30fa83f8","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:07:36.472Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-28 15:07:25 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | 申广亮 (ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb) [msg:om_x100b5343ac71bca0c3b603630cb0cef, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5343ac71bca0c3b603630cb0cef\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb\",\n  \"sender\": \"申广亮\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-28 15:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"申广亮 (ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb\",\n  \"name\": \"申广亮\"\n}\n```\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_4c3a7091abd7f659356ba8680ab939eb Sat 2026-03-28 15:07 GMT+8] 申广亮: /workspace/projects/media/inbound/03173df4-bcdb-4c56-bf21-d1c1696c8046.jpg\nDescription:\nThis image is an English vocabulary learning resource paired with a short Chinese domestic dialogue between two characters, An Jie and Jiang Defu:\n1. A natural Chinese conversational passage forms the context, about sorting old clothes, a school emergency call, and the pair's light exchange.\n2. Key English words, highlighted in yellow and integrated into the Chinese text: **toss, possess, possession, compromise, concept, emergency, message, mind, positive, ambition** each have their part of sp"}],"timestamp":1774681656469}}
{"type":"message","id":"c259d8b8","parentId":"276d6462","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:07:40.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人发了一张图片，描述说这是一个英语词汇学习资源，包含一个中文对话。让我下载图片看看具体内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人，让我先看看这张图片的内容！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d334519d0c819c37cec5baae88072","name":"feishu_im_bot_image","arguments":{"message_id":"om_x100b5343ac71bca0c3b603630cb0cef","file_key":"03173df4-bcdb-4c56-bf21-d1c1696c8046.jpg","type":"image"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":9705,"output":133,"cacheRead":34752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44590,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774681656472}}
