{"type":"message","id":"314141ca","parentId":"0e46b22c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T07:46:45.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，HTTP 服务器已经启动了。现在我需要让主人知道如何访问。\n\n如果这台机器有公网IP，主人可以直接通过 http://<IP>:8080/us-stock-learning.html 访问。\n\n如果没有公网IP，需要内网穿透工具。让我先获取一下机器的IP地址。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3368e42e0f7927bec0c2dbb53b19","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"hostname -I"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":227,"output":140,"cacheRead":53760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54127,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774684002685}}
