{"type":"message","id":"4fbca65c","parentId":"bf0996e3","timestamp":"2026-03-28T08:00:57.670Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"安装进度现在约 28.4%，还在继续中。\n\n我现在应该：\n1. 继续让后台安装运行\n2. 给主人提供快速使用的方案\n\n最快的方案是把 HTML 代码直接给主人，让他复制到 CodePen 或 JSFiddle。HTML 文件我已经读过了，我可以直接给主人。\n\n或者我可以尝试用其他方式，比如使用 data URI，但那个对移动端可能不太友好。\n\n最好的方式是把文件路径告诉主人，并且给他建议使用的在线工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"后台安装进度：28.4%，继续运行中 ✅\n\n---\n\n**🚀 快速方案（推荐使用 CodePen，最简单）：**\n\n### 方法 1：使用 CodePen（1分钟搞定）\n\n1. 打开 https://codepen.io/pen/\n2. 点击 \"Change Editor View\" → \"Full Page\" \n3. 把下面的代码复制粘贴进去：\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>英语学习：美股新闻</title>\n    <style>\n        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            padding: 20px;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            padding: 30px 25px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 22px;\n            color: #333;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding-bottom: 15px;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .content { line-height: 2.2; font-size: 15px; color: #333; }\n        .english-word {\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #667eea;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fdcb6e 100%);\n            padding: 2px 6px;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin: 0 2px;\n        }\n        .word-info {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            color: #e74c3c;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            margin-left: 2px;\n        }\n        .subtitle {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #667eea;\n            margin-top: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n        .vocab-table {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n        .vocab-table th, .vocab-table td {\n            padding: 12px 10px;\n            text-align: left;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n            font-size: 13px;\n        }\n        .vocab-table th {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n        .vocab-table td:first-child { font-weight: 700; color: #667eea; }\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            body { padding: 10px; }\n            .container { padding: 20px 15px; }\n            h1 { font-size: 18px; }\n            .content { line-height: 2; font-size: 14px; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>📚 英语学习：美股新闻</h1>\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <p><strong>US Stock</strong> <span class=\"english-word\">Sell-off</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.抛售）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Devastates</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.重创，现在时）</span> <strong>Tech Giants</strong></p>\n            <p>最近一周，<span class=\"english-word\">Persistent</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.持续的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Inflation</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.通胀）</span>持续 <span class=\"english-word\">Surging</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.飙升，现在分词）</span>，市场 <span class=\"english-word\">Concerned</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.担心的）</span>利率会在更长时间内保持 <span class=\"english-word\">Elevated</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.升高的）</span>。大型科技股遭遇 <span class=\"english-word\">Severe</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.严重的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Setback</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.挫折）</span>，\"美股七巨头\"整体市值累计 <span class=\"english-word\">Evaporated</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.蒸发，过去式）</span>超过 8500 亿美元。</p>\n            <p>Meta 本周 <span class=\"english-word\">Plunged</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.暴跌，过去式）</span>超 11%，创下自 2025 年 10 月以来最差 <span class=\"english-word\">Weekly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.每周的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Performance</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.表现）</span>。此前该公司在一桩 <span class=\"english-word\">Landmark</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.标志性的）</span>社交媒体 <span class=\"english-word\">Lawsuit</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.诉讼案）</span>中败诉。陪审团裁定 Meta 和谷歌 <span class=\"english-word\">Negligent</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.疏忽的）</span>，未能保护平台上的未成年用户。Alphabet 周内 <span class=\"english-word\">Declined</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.下降，过去式）</span>近 9%。</p>\n            <p>微软下跌 6.5%，可能迎来 2008 年以来最差 <span class=\"english-word\">Quarterly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.季度的）</span>表现，软件股受冲击 <span class=\"english-word\">Particularly</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adv.特别地）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Severe</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.严重的）</span>。英伟达和亚马逊均下跌约 3%，特斯拉五个交易日内 <span class=\"english-word\">Dropped</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.下跌，过去式）</span>近 2%。</p>\n            <p>此次抛售潮前，Alphabet <span class=\"english-word\">Released</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.发布，过去式）</span>新的研究，公布了一款旨在降低 AI 内存占用的 <span class=\"english-word\">Algorithm</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.算法）</span>，引发 <span class=\"english-word\">Semiconductor</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.半导体）</span>板块 <span class=\"english-word\">Volatility</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.震荡）</span>。</p>\n            <p>受油价 <span class=\"english-word\">Surge</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.飙升）</span>推高 <span class=\"english-word\">Inflationary</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.通胀的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Expectations</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.预期）</span>、债券收益率 <span class=\"english-word\">Rising</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.上升的）</span>影响，成长股本周遭 <span class=\"english-word\">Battered</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.重创，过去式/被动语态）</span>。投资者认为，<span class=\"english-word\">Federal</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.联邦的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Reserve</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.储备）</span>将无法按预期在今年 <span class=\"english-word\">Cut</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.降息，原形）</span>。</p>\n            <p>苹果是\"美股七巨头\"中唯一 <span class=\"english-word\">Modest</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.适度的）</span> <span class=\"english-word\">Gain</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.涨幅）</span>的个股。报道称，苹果计划将 Siri 语音助手 <span class=\"english-word\">Open</span><span class=\"word-info\">（v.开放，原形/不定式）</span>给 ChatGPT 之外的其他 <span class=\"english-word\">Competing</span><span class=\"word-info\">（adj.竞争的）</span> AI <span class=\"english-word\">Service</span><span class=\"word-info\">（n.服务）</span>。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"subtitle\">📖 词汇表</div>\n        <table class=\"vocab-table\">\n            <thead><tr><th>单词</th><th>词性</th><th>中文释义</th></tr></thead>\n            <tbody>\n                <tr><td>Sell-off</td><td>n.</td><td>抛售</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Devastates</td><td>v.</td><td>重创（现在时）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Persistent</td><td>adj.</td><td>持续的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Inflation</td><td>n.</td><td>通胀</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Surging</td><td>v.</td><td>飙升（现在分词）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Concerned</td><td>adj.</td><td>担心的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Elevated</td><td>adj.</td><td>升高的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Severe</td><td>adj.</td><td>严重的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Setback</td><td>n.</td><td>挫折</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Evaporated</td><td>v.</td><td>蒸发（过去式）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Plunged</td><td>v.</td><td>暴跌（过去式）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Weekly</td><td>adj.</td><td>每周的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Performance</td><td>n.</td><td>表现</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Landmark</td><td>adj.</td><td>标志性的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Lawsuit</td><td>n.</td><td>诉讼案</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Negligent</td><td>adj.</td><td>疏忽的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Declined</td><td>v.</td><td>下降（过去式）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Quarterly</td><td>adj.</td><td>季度的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Particularly</td><td>adv.</td><td>特别地</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Dropped</td><td>v.</td><td>下跌（过去式）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Released</td><td>v.</td><td>发布（过去式）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Algorithm</td><td>n.</td><td>算法</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Semiconductor</td><td>n.</td><td>半导体</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Volatility</td><td>n.</td><td>震荡</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Surge</td><td>n.</td><td>飙升</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Inflationary</td><td>adj.</td><td>通胀的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Expectations</td><td>n.</td><td>预期</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Rising</td><td>adj.</td><td>上升的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Battered</td><td>v.</td><td>重创（过去式/被动）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Federal</td><td>adj.</td><td>联邦的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Reserve</td><td>n.</td><td>储备</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Cut</td><td>v.</td><td>降息（原形）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Modest</td><td>adj.</td><td>适度的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Gain</td><td>n.</td><td>涨幅</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Open</td><td>v.</td><td>开放（原形/不定式）</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Competing</td><td>adj.</td><td>竞争的</td></tr>\n                <tr><td>Service</td><td>n.</td><td>服务</td></tr>\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n4. 点击 \"Save\" 或 \"Fork\"\n5. 然后就可以分享链接了！🎉\n\n---\n\n让我继续监控后台安装进度："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d3