{"type":"message","id":"ff82f2cd","parentId":"eab2fba2","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:18:26.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人问我能不能直接执行上传到飞书云盘。让我看看我有没有飞书相关的工具。\n\n我查看了可用的工具列表，确实有 `feishu_drive_file` 工具，它可以：\n- list（列出文件）\n- upload（上传文件）- 支持 file_path 或 file_content_base64\n- download（下载文件）\n\n所以我可以直接上传文件到飞书云盘！让我用这个工具。\n\n主人之前让我上传时，我尝试过但需要用户授权。让我再试一次，看看能不能成功。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当然可以主人！让我直接用飞书工具上传文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d33bcd376a39cb99ebcc24c49fbaa","name":"feishu_drive_file","arguments":{"action":"upload","file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/us-stock-learning.html"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":297,"output":262,"cacheRead":86400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86959,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774689496953}}
