{"type":"message","id":"e74b4f5c","parentId":"8e0ca69b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T14:19:41.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"微信页面显示了验证页面。根据 SKILL.md 中的说明，需要检查是否有 Mandatory Login（强制登录）的情况。这里看起来是一个验证页面，需要用户手动完成验证。\n\n根据安全指南：\n- If Mandatory Login Is Detected:\n  1. Stop the automation task immediately.\n  2. DO NOT close the browser or the current page (keep the session active).\n  3. Inform the user that manual verification is required.\n  4. Provide the VNC link (the browser preview URL below) so they can verify.\n\n我需要告诉主人需要手动完成验证，并提供浏览器预览链接。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，微信文章需要通过验证才能访问。这是一个安全验证页面，需要手动完成验证。\n\n让我保持浏览器会话，你需要：\n\n**步骤：**\n1. 访问这个链接完成验证（浏览器预览地址）：\n   `🖥️   [点击预览](https://code.coze.cn/browser/7621461512944336905)`\n\n2. 验证完成后告诉我\n\n3. 我会重新获取文章内容\n\n---\n\n**说明：**\n- 验证是微信的安全机制\n- 浏览器会话已保持，验证后可以直接获取内容\n- 预览链接可以让你在浏览器中完成验证\n\n主人准备好验证时告诉我！🎀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":277,"output":404,"cacheRead":91008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774707575199}}
