{"type":"message","id":"1156ce95","parentId":"6bd4a108","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:49:42.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"CLI 版本是 1.3.6，大于要求的 1.2.30，满足要求。现在需要让用户选择 China 还是 Global 站点，然后登录。根据技能说明，我需要问用户选择哪个站点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **CLI 安装成功！** 版本 1.3.6 ✓\n\n---\n\n### 2. 请主人选择站点\n\n**请告诉琪琪你想用哪个 EdgeOne 站点：**\n\n- **China** — 中国区站点（需要国内账号）\n- **Global** — 全球站点\n\n选择哪个呢？🎀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":635,"output":160,"cacheRead":96317,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97112,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774712977738}}
