{"type":"message","id":"b5cd2d06","parentId":"5fd970fe","timestamp":"2026-03-28T15:50:18.282Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了 API Token：nErJUE/2bCEGv96OAhb6FOBYThbqh+FzKmzXoT2ptXs=\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 先问用户是否要保存这个 Token 到本地\n2. 然后部署项目\n\n根据 SKILL.md，我应该在部署前问用户是否要保存 Token。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到 Token！\n\n**是否要保存这个 Token 以便下次使用？**\n\n- **Yes** — 保存到 `.edgeone/.token`（下次部署自动使用）\n- **No** — 这次部署使用，下次需要重新输入\n\n你想保存吗？🎀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":620,"output":209,"cacheRead":96317,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774713012781}}
