{"type":"message","id":"8c1f9791","parentId":"21d533f5","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:15:28.564Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I'm having trouble finding the correct API. Let me check if there are any environment variables or config files that might have the project URL, or try to check if there's a way to query the project status using the project ID directly.Actually, I should just be honest with the user that I cannot query the project preview URL through the CLI or API due to the limitations. The Gitee type project needs to be triggered from the control plane or through Gitee webhook.Let me be transparent with the user about this limitation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，抱歉！经过多种尝试：\n\n**琪琪无法通过 CLI 或 API 查询到 mynews 项目的预览地址**\n\n原因：\n1. EdgeOne CLI 没有查询历史部署的功能\n2. API 接口需要正确的 Action 名称，但我尝试了多种组合都不行\n3. Gitee 类型的项目需要通过控制台或 Gitee Webhook 触发部署\n\n---\n\n**建议：**\n\n1. **你去 EdgeOne 控制台查看部署状态：**\n   - https://console.tencentcloud.com/edgeone/pages\n   - 找到 mynews，点击进入就能看到预览地址\n\n2. **或者在 Gitee 仓库设置 Webhook：**\n   - 让每次 push 后自动触发 EdgeOne 部署\n\n---\n\n琪琪会继续学习，等下次有机会再帮你实现自动化查询！🎀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":168,"output":379,"cacheRead":101245,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101792,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774714520662}}
{"type":"message","id":"5043a9f3","parentId":"8c1f9791","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:20:12.998Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-29 00:20 GMT+8] 那你每次 push 完代码后，直接通过EdgeOne 技能 直接上传并发布吧"}],"timestamp":1774714812990}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1537ce7","parentId":"5043a9f3","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:20:23.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人要求每次 push 代码后，直接使用 EdgeOne 技能上传并发布，而不是依赖 Gitee 类型的项目。\n\n问题是 mynews 是 Gitee 类型，无法通过 CLI 上传。但我可以创建一个新的 Upload 类型的项目来部署。\n\n让我试试创建一个新项目来部署代码。但是每次都创建新项目不太合适。\n\n另一个方案是：主人可以在 EdgeOne 控制台把 mynews 项目从 Gitee 类型改为 Upload 类型，或者删除 mynews 项目，重新创建一个 Upload 类型的新项目。\n\n让我先尝试用 CLI 创建一个新项目来部署：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的主人！问题是 mynews 是 Gitee 类型，无法直接用 CLI 上传。\n\n**解决方案：**\n在 EdgeOne 控制台把 mynews 改成 \"上传\" 类型，或者删除 mynews 后重新创建一个新项目。\n\n让我先试试创建新项目部署：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yfn0uslnohfs_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace && edgeone pages deploy -n mynews-cli -t \"$(cat .edgeone/.token)\" 2>&1","timeout":120000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":97294,"output":338,"cacheRead":4029,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774714812994}}
