{"type":"message","id":"8a160a33","parentId":"b7a0ebbc","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:34:26.213Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"明白了！主人希望的工作流程是：\n1. 修改 Gitee 仓库里的代码（https://gitee.com/siglea/news）\n2. Push 到 Gitee\n3. 通过 EdgeOne CLI 部署\n\n所以我需要：\n1. 先把本地修改推送到 Gitee\n2. 然后从 Gitee 拉取代码（模拟主人修改后的代码）\n3. 用 EdgeOne 部署\n\n但问题是，EdgeOne CLI 部署的是本地代码，而不是从 Gitee 获取的。主人可能是想让我每次从 Gitee pull 代码后再部署？\n\n让我重新理解：主人可能希望的是 - 先 push 代码到 Gitee，然后 EdgeOne 从 Gitee 获取代码进行部署。但 CLI 方式是无法获取 Gitee 代码的。\n\n实际上，CLI 部署方式是上传本地文件夹到 EdgeOne，而不是从 Git 获取。\n\n让我向主人确认一下工作流程。或者，我应该先 pull 代码，看看是否有新的更改，然后部署。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了主人！让我按这个流程来：\n\n1. ✅ 修改仓库代码\n2. ✅ Push 到 Gitee\n3. ✅ 通过 EdgeOne 部署\n\n现在让我先确认一下仓库状态并部署：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l7yf8hno8qx7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace && git status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":111063,"output":456,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111519,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774715651780}}
