{"type":"message","id":"d0028243","parentId":"e2750a5c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:51:05.262Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是显示默认页面。可能是 EdgeOne 的配置问题，或者是 CDN 还没有更新。\n\n让我总结一下当前状态并告诉主人。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"主人，抱歉！让我总结一下当前状态：\n\n**✅ 已完成：**\n1. ✅ 从 Gitee 获取 Keep 盈利文章\n2. ✅ 提取 15 个英文单词\n3. ✅ 创建新的 news HTML 文件\n4. ✅ 更新首页 index.html\n5. ✅ Push 到 Gitee（已成功）\n6. ✅ EdgeOne 部署（已成功）\n\n**文件位置：**\n- `news-2026-03-29-keep-profit.html` ✓\n- `index.html` ✓\n- `README.md` ✓\n\n**Git 状态：**\n```\nf1a49e5 修复文件位置，确保在根目录\n18916a4 添加 Keep 盈利英语学习文章\n```\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 问题：**\n预览地址一直显示默认页面，可能是：\n1. EdgeOne CDN 还在更新中\n2. 域名配置问题\n\n**🔗 最新部署地址：**\nhttps://mynews-cyeblzku.edgeone.cool?eo_token=4a67b9b8ac61c0a5a8965c7ef57d1acb&eo_time=1774716646\n\n**建议：**\n主人可以先去 EdgeOne 控制台查看部署状态，或者稍等几分钟再刷新访问。需要我继续排查吗？🎀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1829,"output":358,"cacheRead":122688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124875,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774716659050}}
