{"type":"message","id":"d57df2ad","parentId":"21bcce9d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:54:42.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"主人让我回顾今天的任务并反思哪里做错了。让我梳理一下今天的工作流程：\n\n1. **最初的英语学习需求**：\n   - 主人发了一张英语单词学习的图片，要求学习这个格式\n   - 我学会了提取英文单词的规则：单个核心词 + 词性释义，嵌入中文句子\n\n2. **创建 HTML 文件**：\n   - 我创建了 `us-stock-learning.html`\n   - 格式符合约定\n\n3. **部署问题开始**：\n   - 主人想要通过 EdgeOne 部署\n   - 我尝试了很多方法\n   - 问题1：下载 kleo-static-files 失败（网络问题）\n   - 问题2：Vercel 需要浏览器认证，无法完成\n   - 问题3：飞书云盘上传需要授权\n   - 问题4：Codepen 方案主人没用\n\n4. **EdgeOne 部署**：\n   - 安装了 edgeone CLI\n   - 部署了 `us-stock-learning.html` 到新项目 `us-stock-learning`\n   - 成功获得了预览地址\n\n5. **尝试查看 mynews 项目**：\n   - 发现 mynews 是 Gitee 类型，CLI 无法直接部署\n   - 创建了新项目 mynews-cli\n\n6. **配置 Gitee 仓库**：\n   - 使用令牌成功推送到 https://gitee.com/siglea/news.git\n   - 但预览地址一直显示默认页面\n\n7. **最后一个问题**：\n   - 文件位置混乱\n   - 部署的 HTML 文件没有正确显示\n\n我意识到部署过程中存在严重的文件管理和同步问题。文件没有正确放置在预期的目录结构中，导致预览页面无法正常渲染。这可能是由于文件夹路径设置错误或同步机制存在缺陷。需要仔细检查文件系统的组织和部署流程，确保每个文件都能准确地定位和展示。 I've encountered deployment challenges with Gitee-type projects. The process involves pushing code to a Gitee repository and attempting EdgeOne deployment, but the preview consistently fails. The deployment appears successful, yet only a default page appears instead of the intended content.\n\nPotential issues seem to stem from configuration complexities, possibly related to EdgeOne's framework detection or build process. I've tried multiple strategies like creating new projects and adjusting file locations, but haven't resolved the underlying problem.\n\nThe core issues appear to be multiple: a misunderstood approach to static site deployment, ineffective use of EdgeOne skills, persistent configuration complications, and a breakdown in the established project workflow.\n\nKey mistakes include pushing unnecessary files, selecting an inappropriate project type, losing track of a critical preview address, and failing to clearly communicate with the project owner about techn